<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Congratulations! You've Earned Referral Tokens!</title>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
</head>
<body>
  {{> header}}

  <div style="padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333;">
    <h1 style="color: #28a745;">Congratulations!</h1>

    {{#if userName}}
    <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>
    {{else}}
    <p>Hi there,</p>
    {{/if}}

    <p>Great news! Someone you referred has just joined Only35, and you've earned a reward!</p>

    <div style="background: #d4edda; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #28a745; text-align: center;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #155724;">You've been awarded</p>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; color: #155724;">{{tokensAwarded}} Tokens</p>
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #155724;">as a thank you for spreading the word!</p>
    </div>

    <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;"><strong>How to use your tokens:</strong></p>
      <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li style="margin: 5px 0;">Use tokens to enhance your Only35 experience</li>
        <li style="margin: 5px 0;">Tokens can be used for premium features and services</li>
        <li style="margin: 5px 0;">Keep referring friends to earn more tokens!</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
      Thank you for being a valued member of our community and helping us grow!
    </p>

    <p style="color: #6c757d; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 40px;">
      If you have any questions about your tokens, please contact our support team.
    </p>
  </div>

  {{> footer}}
</body>
</html>
